{"type":"step-attempt","step":"request-review","sessionId":"279a7d8d-b90e-4f65-8e2d-dee5b97724d8","outcome":{"verdict":"approve","findingsPath":"specrunner/changes/write-scope-bypass-closure/request-review-result-001.md","error":null,"toolResult":{"ok":true,"verdict":"approve","findings":[],"observations":[{"severity":"low","file":"src/core/step/commit-push.ts","title":"commitScopedPaths も pathspec なし commit を使用（スコープ外）","rationale":"並列 round coordinator の commitScopedPaths（line 447）も git commit -m commitMessage（pathspec なし）を使用しており、理論的に同一の index 混入問題を持つ。ただし request で明示的にスコープ外とされており（partitionRoundChanges による変更セット制限が異なる文脈での防衛となっている）、独立した確認が必要。本 request の実装完了後に同欠陥の有無を個別確認すると良い。","line":447}]},"followUpAttempts":0,"transientRetryAttempts":0,"addedTurns":{"reportRetry":0,"postWork":0,"outputRepair":0}},"startedAt":"2026-07-21T23:16:18.151Z","endedAt":"2026-07-21T23:19:44.855Z","commitOid":"e667a34d97e4e0bb1d585c9d81f786fe67729f17"}
