{"type":"step-attempt","step":"design","sessionId":"33653197-8d8c-4fa0-ba7d-df64f5bee92f","outcome":{"verdict":"success","findingsPath":null,"error":null,"toolResult":{"ok":true,"reason":"Wrote design.md, spec.md, tasks.md under specrunner/changes/write-scope-bypass-closure/ on branch change/write-scope-bypass-closure-be8366eb.\n\nDesign thesis (D1): extend the write-scope enforcement surface from \"worktree diff\" to \"the full effect of the step (worktree + index + self-commit)\", closing the 3 confirmed bypass routes at the same commit boundary.\n\nKey decisions:\n- D2 self-commit inspection: enumerate headBeforeStep..HEAD, apply per-mode rule (scoped: changed − declared − managed; guarded: findWriteScopeViolations), violation → quarantine committed diff + NO push + WRITE_SCOPE_VIOLATION halt; keep local commit (no git reset). Fail-closed on enumeration error.\n- D3 index-contamination block: scoped commit uses `git commit -- <declared+managed>` (partial-commit records worktree content of listed paths only), staged-detection scoped to same pathspec; guarded keeps whole-index; explicit no-fallback for empty scoped pathspec.\n- D4 scoped residual halt: throw after quarantine+restore instead of continue (relies on verified invariant: finalizeStepArtifacts runs before deriveStepCompletion, so halt suppresses result adoption).\n- D5 add findScopedCommitViolations to write-scope.ts leaf (managedPaths injected). D6 generalize quarantine to a diff range. D7 pass scope context to shared tail.\n\nVerified against current code (not just the attested list): executor ordering (executor.ts:438-461 vs 483), makeCommitFailHalt preserving err.code (step-halt.ts:305-316), commitFinalState no-op-on-clean, local.ts diffPathsBetweenCommits shape, and the real-git test harness (makeRealGitNoPushSpawnFn in test-materialize-boundary.test.ts) referenced for T-10 destructive confirmation.\n\nspec.md: 5 Requirements with Given/When/Then scenarios covering all acceptance criteria. tasks.md: T-01..T-11 (write-scope fn, quarantine range, range helper, scoped pathspec, self-commit check, residual halt, docstrings, updated existing tests TC-023/quarantine-03, new mock unit tests, real-git integration/破壊確認, verification). Code edits deferred to implementer as instructed.","status":"success"},"followUpAttempts":0,"transientRetryAttempts":0,"addedTurns":{"reportRetry":0,"postWork":0,"outputRepair":0}},"startedAt":"2026-07-21T23:19:46.883Z","endedAt":"2026-07-21T23:31:43.818Z","commitOid":"7d929193f813f5e0ff78b7ed03520b2c5fd8110c"}
